name: Jamil Ur Rahman
desc: Front-End Web Developer with 03+ years in JavaScript and React.js. I build dynamic, responsive web applications and am pursuing an MS in Data Sciences.
aboutDesc: A dedicated Software Engineer with expertise in React.js and a strong background in Front-End Development. At Smart Forum, I've successfully delivered high-quality software solutions and contributed to critical projects, demonstrating my problem-solving skills and commitment to continuous learning. My certifications in Data Science, Power BI, and MySQL further enhance my technical capabilities. I am passionate about leveraging technology to solve real-world problems and eager to bring my dedication and innovation to new challenges.
